name: aisbreaker-core-browser
description: This package contains core services and adapters for AIsBreaker with dependeny to the AIsBreaker API. For modern web browsers. AIsBreaker provides an easy-to-use and service-agnostic API to access different AI services (like OpenAI/ChatGPT API, Open-Assistant API, Google Bart API and many more) in a uniform way. More details: https://aisbreaker.org/
author: aisbreaker
